<refnamediv><refname>dnn_decode_segmentation</refname><refpurpose>Convert class-score tensors to a label mask.</refpurpose></refnamediv>
<refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>mask = dnn_decode_segmentation(output)</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv>
<refsection><title>Description</title><para><function>dnn_decode_segmentation</function> selects the highest scoring class for every pixel in an H-by-W-by-C tensor.</para></refsection>
<refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
scores = cat(3, [1 0; 0 1], [0 1; 1 0]);
mask = dnn_decode_segmentation(scores);
]]></programlisting></refsection>
